## Bin Probability

## Bin Distribution

Calling bin_distribution returns an object of class bindis which is a data frame.  The frame
has the probability distribution for the number of trials with the probability of success specified
in the parameters "trials" and "prob".

bin_distribution(trials = 5, prob = 0.5)

